    public class NeutronFirewallPolicyRule
extends AbstractNeutronFirewallPolicy
    A Neutron Firewall (FwaaS) : Firewall Policy Entity.

    This is the child class of AbstractNeutronFirewallPolicy which is used by `rule_insert/rule_remove` calls - which doesn't require JsonRootName firewall_policy.
